{"tid":1289884,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯議員 你地派蛇齋餅糭派得專業啲得唔得？","createTime":"2019-07-06T09:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T15:08:03.000Z","uid":246649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ecdb9c6c1b797b799c2c317ae7d6f6101b651d","tid":1289884,"uid":246649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"話說我係一個補習老師<br />\n早排我學生同我講話佢要跟一個民建聯議員去迪士尼<br />\n講撚到幾鬼期待幾鬼開心<br />\n講到好似成世冇去過迪士尼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲同我請埋假 <br />\n<br />\n然後今日同佢講起：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：學生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：喂 你早排去迪士尼去成點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唉 唔好提喇 晨咁早交左表 去到要入迪士尼果日 佢先話我知唔記得幫我地交表 空歡喜一場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：交咩表？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：果啲咩低收入家庭資助掛 唔知啊 佢話填左就有得去嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁佢唔係儲完一大堆咁交嘅咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔知呀 總之佢交漏左我地果份啦 好失望 老豆老母話下次都係唔投佢 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c12c61f78540447fdbff57e5f3da8573fecbe3","tid":1289884,"uid":262072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"你請佢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2342798c3367f83c2946fcaf992872f022b4adc","tid":1289884,"uid":246649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97c12c61f78540447fdbff57e5f3da8573fecbe3","tid":1289884,"uid":262072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"你請佢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:08:03.000Z","msg":"